chase � above ,500K, ,500K & ,500K. Complimentary Dior gift wrapping service. Discover Dior Homme Parfum reinvented by Francis Kurkdjian, Perfume Creative Director. A men''s fragrance crafted around a dual iris note, both airy and intense. The olfactory interpretation of modern masculinity, a balance between strength and tenderness. Dior Homme Parfum is the story of an encounter: the smooth, carnal notes of iris meet powerful ambery wood accords. A trail that expresses a masculine twist on the flower, with an overdose of iris creating an addictive, sensual, and elegant composition. The structure of the fragrance, airy yet dense, takes shape in a monolithic bottle with clean lines and a sensual color gradient. #21722 ALCOHOL � PARFUM (FRAGRANCE) � AQUA (WATER) � CITRUS AURANTIUM BERGAMIA (BERGAMOT) PEEL OIL � TETRAMETHYL ACETYLOCTAHYDRONAPHTHALENES � LIMONENE � LINALYL ACETATE � LINALOOL � COUMARIN � ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE � PINENE � BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE � CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL � LAVANDULA OIL/EXTRACT � POGOSTEMON CABLIN OIL � GERANYL ACETATE � DIETHYLAMINO HYDROXYBENZOYL HEXYL BENZOATE � CAMPHOR � CITRAL � BETA-CARYOPHYLLENE � TERPINEOL � TERPINOLENE � GERANIOL � ALPHA-TERPINENE � ROSE KETONES � CINNAMOMUM ZEYLANICUM BARK OIL � CINNAMAL � FARNESOL � EUGENOL � ISOEUGENOL � CI 47005 (YELLOW 10) � CI 14700 (RED 4) � CI 60730 (EXT. VIOLET 2) 1. Awaken the senses with the invigorating notes of Dior Homme shower gel. 2. Soften your skin with Dior Homme after-shave balm. 3. Refresh with Dior Homme deodorant. 4. Spray on Dior Homme Parfum for the finishing touch. Heart Notes AMBERY ACCORD A gourmet ambery accord where the density of patchouli meets a powerful vetiver, mingled with a note of coumarin and dry accents of cut hay. Privacy Policy Terms and conditions Cookies Policy Cookies are in use on this site These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly. These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising. These cookies are set by a range of social media services that we have added to the site to enable you to share our content with your friends and networks. They are capable of tracking your browser across other sites and building up a profile of your interests. This may impact the content and messages you see on other websites you visit. If you do not allow these cookies you may not be able to use or see these sharing tools. These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.', NULL, 3810000.0, 'Pria', 'Pagi / Siang', 'Office / Formal', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dior.com/en_id/beauty/products/dior-homme-parfum-Y0997193.html', 0.0, 0.0, 'Parfum', 'Lime, Bergamot', 'Violet, Rose, Sage', 'Patchouli, Vetiver, Amber', 'Woody, Floral, Citrus, Oriental', 'Musim Semi', 'Sangat Tahan Lama (8+ jam)', 'Sangat Kuat (Loud)');
INSERT INTO public.perfumes (nama_parfum, brand, description, notes, harga, gender_target, waktu_penggunaan, occasion, wangi_vibe, url_foto, url_produk, rating_value, rating_count, concentration, top_notes, middle_notes, base_notes, main_accords, cuaca_musim, longevity, sillage) VALUES ('Dior Homme Sport', 'DIOR', 'Eau de Toilette - Fresh, Woody and Spicy Notes description ingredients application tips olfactory notes description Energetic and elegant, the new Dior Homme Sport eau de toilette combines fresh vivacity and charm tinted with sensuality for a duo that strikes like a boxer''s uppercut. Vibrant, explosive, the opening signature of Dior Homme Sport is marked by citrus and the open air, freshness and movement. For this new Dior Homme Sport, the Dior Perfumer-Creator chose to tinge the composition with warm and amber notes, wrap it in spices and round it out with woody notes. The confident trail of Dior Homme Sport incarnates a masculinity entwined with smooth, noble qualtiy. The new Dior Homme Sport eau de toilette plays freshness and sensuality. It''s a luminous scent enriched with a new, lasting impression that takes hold and lingers like a caress. ingredients #16128 ALCOHOL � PARFUM (FRAGRANCE) � AQUA (WATER) � LIMONENE � LINALOOL � BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE � HEXYL CINNAMAL � CITRAL � CITRONELLOL � TRIETHYL CITRATE � EUGENOL � PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE � CINNAMAL � GERANIOL � TRIS(TETRAMETHYLHYDROXYPIPERIDINOL) CITRATE � EVERNIA FURFURACEA (TREEMOSS) EXTRACT � CI 14700 (RED 4) � CI 47005 (YELLOW 10) � CI 60730 (EXT. VIOLET 2) application tips Prolong the trail of Dior Homme Sport eau de toilette with the Dior Homme ritual: 1. Awaken the senses with the invigorating notes of Dior Homme shower gel. 2. Soften your skin with Dior Homme after-shave balm. 3. Get that fresh feeling with Dior Homme spray deodorant. olfactory notes Base Notes Frankincense and Woody Notes Frankincense appears for the first time at the heart of Dior Homme Sport, heightened and generous. It inspires a heavenly intensity that melds with the woods and amber, emblematic signatures of Dior Homme. Heart Notes Elemi and Pink Pepper This thunderous departure is enriched with intense fresh notes, like the ultra-powerful, resinous and lemony Elemi that enters into dialogue with the juicy citrus and further heightens its expressiveness. Explosive, the peppery spice of Pink Pepper joins in the dance of the new fragrance''s composition. Top Notes Reggio di Calabria Bergamot An absolute signature of vibrant top notes, Reggio di Calabria Bergamot is a juicy, zesty and distinguished gust of wind, upheld by an Italian Lemon note. It''s a knock to the senses, an appeal to an irresistible freshness now propelled by a vibrant aldehyde note. A MEMBER OF THE UNION FOR ETHICAL BIOTRADE, DIOR IS COMMITTED TO A SOURCING THAT IS RESPECTFUL OF NATURE AND COMMUNITIES. These products might interest you IDR C099600670 DIOR Y0996472 950000.0 true MEN�S FRAGRANCE SAUVAGE Bath & Shaving Sauvage Shower Gel C099600670 1.0 regular Sauvage Shower Gel Shower Gel - Cleanses and Refreshes 250 mL IDR F001802000 DIOR Y0018020 700000.0 false MEN�S FRAGRANCE Sauvage Sauvage F001802000 1.0 regular Sauvage Stick deodorant 75 g description ingredients application tips olfactory notes description Energetic and elegant, the new Dior Homme Sport eau de toilette combines fresh vivacity and charm tinted with sensuality for a duo that strikes like a boxer''s uppercut. Vibrant, explosive, the opening signature of Dior Homme Sport is marked by citrus and the open air, freshness and movement. For this new Dior Homme Sport, the Dior Perfumer-Creator chose to tinge the composition with warm and amber notes, wrap it in spices and round it out with woody notes. The confident trail of Dior Homme Sport incarnates a masculinity entwined with smooth, noble qualtiy. The new Dior Homme Sport eau de toilette plays freshness and sensuality. It''s a luminous scent enriched with 