these services may not function properly. These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising. These cookies are set by a range of social media services that we have added to the site to enable...', NULL, 1290000.0, 'Wanita', 'Pagi / Siang', 'Office / Formal', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dior.com/en_id/beauty/products/miss-dior-eau-de-parfum-mini-miss-solid-perfume-refill-Y3997007.html', 0.0, 0.0, 'Eau de Parfum (EDP)', 'Citron, Lime', 'Rose, Lily, Peony', 'Tonka, Sandalwood, Musk', 'Woody, Floral, Citrus, Oriental', 'Musim Semi', 'Tahan Lama (4-8 jam)', 'Kuat (Moderate-Heavy)');
INSERT INTO public.perfumes (nama_parfum, brand, description, notes, harga, gender_target, waktu_penggunaan, occasion, wangi_vibe, url_foto, url_produk, rating_value, rating_count, concentration, top_notes, middle_notes, base_notes, main_accords, cuaca_musim, longevity, sillage) VALUES ('Miss Dior Parfum Mini Miss Solid Perfume', 'DIOR', 'Alcohol-Free Fragrance Stick - Intense Floral, Fruity and Woody Notes description ingredients application tips olfactory notes description Miss Dior Parfum is reinvented in an alcohol-free solid perfume with a sheer finish, to apply the intense floral, fruity and woody notes of the fragrance directly to the skin. A mini-object with maxi-effects, Miss Dior Parfum solid perfume is highly concentrated to prolong the scent of Miss Dior Parfum. Infused with rose wax, the stick melts comfortably onto the skin, without any sticky residue, leaving it fragrant and hydrated. The solid perfume is applied on pulse points (neck, d�collet�, wrists) on its own or as complementary touch-ups to the spray. Miss Dior Parfum Mini Miss is housed in a jacquard case woven with the houndstooth pattern, a signature of the Dior wardrobe style. A reflection of the elegant and joyful Miss Dior spirit, it is the perfect on-the-go couture accessory. ingredients #20962 OCTYLDODECANOL � COCO-CAPRYLATE/CAPRATE � PARFUM (FRAGRANCE) � DIBUTYL LAUROYL GLUTAMIDE � PHYTOSTERYL/OCTYLDODECYL LAUROYL GLUTAMATE � DIBUTYL ETHYLHEXANOYL GLUTAMIDE � LINALOOL � LIMONENE � BENZYL SALICYLATE � CITRONELLOL � DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL � GERANIOL � ROSA CENTIFOLIA FLOWER WAX � ROSA DAMASCENA FLOWER WAX � COUMARIN � HEXYL CINNAMAL � PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE � TOCOPHEROL � POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE � CITRAL � TRIMETHYLOLPROPANE TRIISOSTEARATE � BENZYL BENZOATE � CI 15985 (YELLOW 6 LAKE) � BENZYL ALCOHOL � CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES) � ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE � CI 15850 (RED 7 LAKE) � CI 15850 (RED 6) � PROPYL GALLATE application tips Apply the fragrance stick on pulse points - wrists, neck and d�collet� - alone or as a complement to spray fragrances. The texture leaves no color on the skin, only the floral, fruity and woody scent of Miss Dior Parfum. Do not apply on lips. olfactory notes Base Notes AMBERY WOODS A sensually and solidly constructed woody-ambery composition, anchored by a full and refined patchouli, darkened by a dense and binding Alaskan cedar. A forest floor carpeted with moss seems to envelop the composition. Heart Notes STAR JASMINE Floral accords dominated by the intensity of a jasmine note, tailor-made for Dior. They are infused with vibrant, sweet and juicy notes, reminiscent of plump, succulent wild strawberries. Francis Kurkdjian wanted to reproduce the specific notes extracted from the jasmine of 1947, the year Miss Dior was born. A jasmine with rare facets was thus chosen and given special treatment, both in terms of harvesting conditions and the use of new technologies. An unprecedented process* that imparts fruity accents, tinged with strawberries, peaches and apricots, faithful to the jasmine of yesteryear while preserving all of its radiance. * At Dior. Top Notes SPARKLING MANDARIN Sparkling and juicy notes of mandarin. description ingredients application tips olfactory notes description Miss Dior Parfum is reinvented in an alcohol-free solid perfume with a sheer finish, to apply the intense floral, fruity and woody notes of the fragrance directly to the skin. A mini-object with maxi-effects, Miss Dior Parfum solid perfume is highly concentrated to prolong the scent of Miss Dior Parfum. Infused with rose wax, the stick melts comfortably onto the skin, without any sticky residue, leaving it fragrant and hydrated. The solid perfume is applied on pulse points (neck, d�collet�, wrists) on its own or as complementary touch-ups to the spray. Miss Dior Parfum Mini Miss is housed in a jacquard case woven with the houndstooth pattern, a signature of the Dior wardrobe style. A reflection of the elegant and jo