GLUTAMIDE � PHYTOSTERYL/OCTYLDODECYL LAUROYL GLUTAMATE � DIBUTYL ETHYLHEXANOYL GLUTAMIDE � LINALOOL � LIMONENE � BENZYL SALICYLATE � CITRONELLOL � DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL � GERANIOL � ROSA CENTIFOLIA FLOWER WAX � ROSA DAMASCENA FLOWER WAX � COUMARIN � HEXYL CINNAMAL � PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE � TOCOPHEROL � POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE � CITRAL � TRIMETHYLOLPROPANE TRIISOSTEARATE � BENZYL BENZOATE � CI 15985 (YELLOW 6 LAKE) � BENZYL ALCOHOL � CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES) � ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE � CI 15850 (RED 7 LAKE) � CI 1...', NULL, 1910000.0, 'Wanita', 'Malam', 'Office / Formal', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dior.com/en_id/beauty/products/miss-dior-parfum-mini-miss-solid-perfume-Y0998029.html', 0.0, 0.0, 'Parfum', 'Citron, Lime, Mandarin', 'Jasmine, Rose, Sage', 'Patchouli, Cedar, Amber', 'Woody, Floral, Citrus, Oriental', 'Musim Semi', 'Sangat Tahan Lama (8+ jam)', 'Sangat Kuat (Loud)');
